           move      zero                 to   w-rg2-bef-scf (1)      .
           move      spaces               to   w-rg2-bef-scf-des (1)  .
           move      spaces               to   w-rg2-bef-scf-fil (1)  .
           move      spaces               to   w-rg2-bef-scf-ccc (1)  .
