      *                  * Aggiornamento totali scadenze               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           add       w-rg2-iiv-scf (1)    to   w-tes-tiv-scf (1)      .
           add       w-rg2-imp-scf (1)    to   w-tes-tot-scf (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Eventuale aggiustamento dell'ultima scaden- *
      *                  * za                                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test se ultima scadenza                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-car-cat-scf-ctr    not  = w-clc-tbl-scd-nts
                     go to car-cat-scf-500.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test se calcolo scadenze in valuta      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-sgl-vlt (1)    =    c-sgl
                     go to car-cat-scf-500.
