      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg2-cur        =    zero or
                     w-cat-rg2-cur        >    9
                     go to vis-tip-rig-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su tipo pagamento                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-trd-scx-mod
                    (w-cat-rg2-cur)       =    spaces
                     go to vis-tip-rig-xml-900.
       vis-tip-rig-xml-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
