      *              * Accettazione valore                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "MX"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "U"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      01                   to   v-car                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-msk                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-alf                  .
