      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Aggiornamenti contabili generati dalla gestione scadenze  *
      *    * fornitori a fronte del movimento di registrazione fattura *
      *    * fornitore                                                 *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Nota : Vedere i commenti per il modulo 'pscf3000' per le  *
      *    *        generalita' sugli aggiornamenti contabili riguar-  *
      *    *        danti la gestione scadenze fornitori.              *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       wrt-mov-cge-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se si e' in modifica di una registrazione che   *
      *              * non aveva generato nessun movimento contabile,  *
      *              * non si genera il movimento contabile            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if       (w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    =    "M"   ) and
                    (w-tes-drg-cge (1)    =    zero or
                     w-tes-npr-cge (1)    =    zero  )
                     go to wrt-mov-cge-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se registrazione contabile da eseguire     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   cge-scf-ftf-snx-000  thru cge-scf-ftf-snx-999    .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se registrazione contabile da non eseguire : u- *
      *              * scita                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cge-scf-ftf-snx    =    "N"
                     go to wrt-mov-cge-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Scrittura movimento per la fattura fornitore    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione work per scrittura testata e*
      *                  * prima riga movimento di CGE                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "NO"                 to   l-cge-300-tip-ope      .
           perform   mdl-agg-cge-cll-000  thru mdl-agg-cge-cll-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Valori per testata registrazione            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo operazione                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "WP"                 to   l-cge-300-tip-ope      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data registrazione                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-drg-cge (1)    to   l-cge-300-dat-reg      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero protocollo                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-npr-cge (1)    to   l-cge-300-num-prt      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Causale                                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-top-cau-cge
                    (w-top-ele-inx)       to   l-cge-300-cod-cau      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Descrizione causale                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-des-cau (1)    to   l-cge-300-des-cau      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Si/No data scadenza                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   l-cge-300-snx-dts      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data scadenza                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   l-cge-300-dat-sca      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data documento                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-ddo-ftf (1)    to   l-cge-300-dat-doc      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero documento                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-ndo-ftf (1)    to   l-cge-300-num-doc      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice numerazione giornale iva         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-ngi-iva (1)    to   l-cge-300-cod-num      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Protocollo iva                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-npt-iva (1)    to   l-cge-300-prt-iva      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Castelletto iva                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-wrt-mov-cge-ctr      .
       wrt-mov-cge-100.
           add       1                    to   w-wrt-mov-cge-ctr      .
           if        w-wrt-mov-cge-ctr    >    6
                     go to wrt-mov-cge-120.
           if        w-tes-iva-cod
                    (1, w-wrt-mov-cge-ctr)
                                          =    zero
                     go to wrt-mov-cge-100.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Imponibile                          *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-iva-ibl
                    (1, w-wrt-mov-cge-ctr)
                                          to   l-cge-300-ibl-iva
                                              (w-wrt-mov-cge-ctr)     .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Aliquota iva                        *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-iva-cod
                    (1, w-wrt-mov-cge-ctr)
                                          to   l-cge-300-cod-iva
                                              (w-wrt-mov-cge-ctr)     .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Imposta                             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-iva-imp
                    (1, w-wrt-mov-cge-ctr)
                                          to   l-cge-300-imp-iva
                                              (w-wrt-mov-cge-ctr)     .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Riciclo                             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     wrt-mov-cge-100.
       wrt-mov-cge-120.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Flag di regime fiscale particolare      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-flg-rfp (1)    to   l-cge-300-flg-rfp      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sigla numerazione                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   l-cge-300-sgl-num      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data acquisizione                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-dat-reg        to   l-cge-300-dat-acq      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Totale documento                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-iva-tdo (1)    to   l-cge-300-tot-doc      .
       wrt-mov-cge-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Start su righe corpo in catena movimenti    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ST"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      1                    to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se start non valida : a fine trattamento    *
      *                  * righe                                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to wrt-mov-cge-300.
       wrt-mov-cge-220.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Next su righe corpo in catena movimenti     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se at end : a fine trattamento righe        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to wrt-mov-cge-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se buffer catena movimenti a spaces: riciclo*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-buf        =    spaces
                     go to wrt-mov-cge-220.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Movimento da buffer catena movimenti a work *
      *                  * per riga w-rig                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rig-buf        to   w-rig                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se riga esistente                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-con (1)    =    spaces
                     go to wrt-mov-cge-220.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Valori per la riga registrazione            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice piano dei conti                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-cod-pdc (1)    to   l-cge-300-cod-pdc      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo archivio                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-tip-con (1)    to   l-cge-300-tip-arc      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice archivio                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-cod-arc (1)    to   l-cge-300-cod-arc      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Commento in riga                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-com-rig (1)    to   l-cge-300-com-rig      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data riferimento                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-dat-rif (1)    to   l-cge-300-dat-rif      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero riferimento                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-num-rif (1)    to   l-cge-300-num-rif      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Dare/Avere                              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-dar-ave (1)    to   l-cge-300-dar-ave      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Importo movimento                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-imp-mov (1)    to   l-cge-300-imp-mov      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Richiamo modulo scrittura CGE               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   mdl-agg-cge-cll-000  thru mdl-agg-cge-cll-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione work per scrittura singola  *
      *                  * riga movimento di CGE                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "N+"                 to   l-cge-300-tip-ope      .
           perform   mdl-agg-cge-cll-000  thru mdl-agg-cge-cll-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione tipo operazione per prossima   *
      *                  * riga movimento di CGE                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "W+"                 to   l-cge-300-tip-ope      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riciclo su prossima riga                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     wrt-mov-cge-220.
       wrt-mov-cge-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Scrittura movimenti per le scadenze             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione numero protocollo              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-npr-cge (1)    to   w-wrt-mov-cge-wnp      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione numero scadenza iniziale       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-npr-scf (1)    to   w-wrt-mov-cge-wns      .
           subtract  1                    from w-wrt-mov-cge-wns      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Start su righe corpo 2 in catena movimenti  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ST"                 to   w-cat-rg2-ope          .
           move      1                    to   w-cat-rg2-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct2-000      thru cll-sub-ct2-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se start non valida : a fine ciclo          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg2-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to wrt-mov-cge-999.
       wrt-mov-cge-310.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Next su righe corpo in catena movimenti     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   w-cat-rg2-ope          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct2-000      thru cll-sub-ct2-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se at end : a fine ciclo                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg2-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to wrt-mov-cge-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Movimento da buffer catena movimenti a work *
      *                  * per riga w-rg2                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rg2-buf        to   w-rg2                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se esistono causale di contabilita' e  *
      *                  * sottoconto per registrazione scadenza       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg2-cau-rsf (1)    =    zero or
                     w-rg2-stc-rsf (1)    =    zero
                     go to wrt-mov-cge-310.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Incremento numero protocollo di contabili-  *
      *                  * ta'                                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-wrt-mov-cge-wnp      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Incremento numero scadenza fornitore        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-wrt-mov-cge-wns      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione work per scrittura testata  *
      *                  * e prima riga movimento di CGE               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "NO"                 to   l-cge-300-tip-ope      .
           perform   mdl-agg-cge-cll-000  thru mdl-agg-cge-cll-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Valori per testata registrazione            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo operazione                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "WP"                 to   l-cge-300-tip-ope      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data registrazione                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-drg-cge (1)    to   l-cge-300-dat-reg      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero protocollo                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-wrt-mov-cge-wnp    to   l-cge-300-num-prt      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Causale                                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg2-cau-rsf (1)    to   l-cge-300-cod-cau      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Descrizione causale                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   l-cge-300-des-cau      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Si/No data scadenza                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   l-cge-300-snx-dts      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data scadenza                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   l-cge-300-dat-sca      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data documento                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-ddo-ftf (1)    to   l-cge-300-dat-doc      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero documento                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "P"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      08                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<"                  to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-wrt-mov-cge-wns    to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   l-cge-300-num-doc      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Valori per prima riga registrazione : Riga  *
      *                  * fornitore                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice piano dei conti                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-cod-fnt-cge (1)
                                          to   l-cge-300-cod-pdc      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo archivio                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "F"                  to   l-cge-300-tip-arc      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice archivio                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-cod-fnt (1)    to   l-cge-300-cod-arc      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Commento in riga                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   l-cge-300-com-rig      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data riferimento                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-ddo-ftf (1)    to   l-cge-300-dat-rif      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero riferimento                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-ndo-ftf (1)    to   l-cge-300-num-rif      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Dare/Avere                              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-ope        =    0003 or
                     w-tes-tip-ope        =    0033 or
                     w-tes-tip-ope        =    0333
                     move  "A"            to   l-cge-300-dar-ave
           else      move  "D"            to   l-cge-300-dar-ave      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Importo movimento                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg2-imp-scf (1)    to   l-cge-300-imp-mov      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Flag di regime fiscale particolare      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   l-cge-300-flg-rfp      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sigla numerazione                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   l-cge-300-sgl-num      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data acquisizione                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-dat-reg        to   l-cge-300-dat-acq      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Richiamo modulo scrittura CGE               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   mdl-agg-cge-cll-000  thru mdl-agg-cge-cll-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione work per scrittura singola  *
      *                  * riga movimento di CGE                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "N+"                 to   l-cge-300-tip-ope      .
           perform   mdl-agg-cge-cll-000  thru mdl-agg-cge-cll-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Scrittura riga di contropartita al fornito- *
      *                  * re                                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo operazione                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "W+"                 to   l-cge-300-tip-ope      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice piano dei conti                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg2-stc-rsf (1)    to   l-cge-300-cod-pdc      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo archivio                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "G"                  to   l-cge-300-tip-arc      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice archivio                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   l-cge-300-cod-arc      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Commento in riga                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   l-cge-300-com-rig      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data riferimento                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   l-cge-300-dat-rif      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero riferimento                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   l-cge-300-num-rif      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Dare/Avere                              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-ope        =    0003 or
                     w-tes-tip-ope        =    0033 or
                     w-tes-tip-ope        =    0333
                     move  "D"            to   l-cge-300-dar-ave
           else      move  "A"            to   l-cge-300-dar-ave      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Importo movimento                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg2-imp-scf (1)    to   l-cge-300-imp-mov      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Flag di regime fiscale particolare      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   l-cge-300-flg-rfp      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sigla numerazione                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   l-cge-300-sgl-num      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data acquisizione                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-dat-reg        to   l-cge-300-dat-acq      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Richiamo modulo scrittura CGE           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   mdl-agg-cge-cll-000  thru mdl-agg-cge-cll-999    .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Riciclo su scansione catena scadenze    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     wrt-mov-cge-310.
       wrt-mov-cge-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Annullamento del movimento di contabilita' generale che   *
      *    * che era stato a suo tempo generato a fronte del movimento *
      *    * di scadenze fornitori di registrazione fattura fornitore  *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       del-mov-cge-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Annullamento registrazione contabile fattura    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se data registrazione o numero protocollo   *
      *                  * di CGE a zero : oltre                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-drg-cge (2)    =    zero or
                     w-tes-npr-cge (2)    =    zero
                     go to del-mov-cge-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Richiamo modulo per cancellazione movimento *
      *                  * di CGE                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DE"                 to   l-cge-300-tip-ope      .
           move      w-tes-drg-cge (2)    to   l-cge-300-dat-reg      .
           move      w-tes-npr-cge (2)    to   l-cge-300-num-prt      .
           perform   mdl-agg-cge-cll-000  thru mdl-agg-cge-cll-999    .
       del-mov-cge-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Annullamento registrazione contabile scadenze   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Start su righe corpo 2 in catena movimenti  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ST"                 to   w-cat-rg2-ope          .
           move      1                    to   w-cat-rg2-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct2-000      thru cll-sub-ct2-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se start non valida : uscita                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg2-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to del-mov-cge-999.
       del-mov-cge-520.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Next su righe corpo in catena movimenti     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   w-cat-rg2-ope          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct2-000      thru cll-sub-ct2-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se at end : a fine ciclo                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg2-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to del-mov-cge-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Movimento da buffer catena movimenti a work *
      *                  * per riga w-rg2                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rg2-buf        to   w-rg2                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se data registrazione o numero protocollo   *
      *                  * di CGE a zero : a riciclo                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg2-drc-rgs (2)    =    zero or
                     w-rg2-npc-rgs (2)    =    zero
                     go to del-mov-cge-580.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Richiamo modulo per cancellazione movimento *
      *                  * di CGE                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DE"                 to   l-cge-300-tip-ope      .
           move      w-rg2-drc-rgs (2)    to   l-cge-300-dat-reg      .
           move      w-rg2-npc-rgs (2)    to   l-cge-300-num-prt      .
           perform   mdl-agg-cge-cll-000  thru mdl-agg-cge-cll-999    .
       del-mov-cge-580.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riciclo per prossima cancellazione          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     del-mov-cge-520.
       del-mov-cge-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Scrittura pareggiamento automatico acconti clienti o for- *
      *    * nitori                                                    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       wrt-pau-acf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se nessun pareggiamento automatico effettuato : *
      *              * uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-imp-pap (1)    =    spaces
                     go to wrt-pau-acf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ciclo di scansione su tabella partite           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-wrt-pau-acf-ctr      .
       wrt-pau-acf-100.
           add       1                    to   w-wrt-pau-acf-ctr      .
           if        w-wrt-pau-acf-ctr    >    w-lpa-num-ele
                     go to wrt-pau-acf-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se l'importo assegnato alla partita e' a    *
      *                  * zero : riciclo                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-lpa-imp-ass
                    (w-wrt-pau-acf-ctr)   =    zero
                     go to wrt-pau-acf-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se i riferimenti della partita sono uguali  *
      *                  * a quelli da forzare : riciclo               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-lpa-dat-rif
                    (w-wrt-pau-acf-ctr)   =    w-lpa-dri-doc and
                     w-lpa-num-rif
                    (w-wrt-pau-acf-ctr)   =    w-lpa-nri-doc
                     go to wrt-pau-acf-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Scansione delle righe di contabilita' rela- *
      *                  * tive alla partita in esame                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Start su file [mgr]                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "SK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "NL"                 to   f-cfr                  .
           move      "ARCRIF"             to   f-key                  .
           move      w-lpa-tip-arc        to   rf-mgr-tip-arc         .
           move      w-lpa-cod-arc        to   rf-mgr-cod-arc         .
           move      w-lpa-dat-rif
                    (w-wrt-pau-acf-ctr)   to   rf-mgr-dat-rif         .
           move      w-lpa-num-rif
                    (w-wrt-pau-acf-ctr)   to   rf-mgr-num-rif         .
           move      zero                 to   rf-mgr-dat-reg         .
           move      zero                 to   rf-mgr-num-prt         .
           move      zero                 to   rf-mgr-num-prg         .
           move      "pgm/cge/fls/ioc/obj/iofmgr"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-mgr                 .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test su esito operazione                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to wrt-pau-acf-300.
       wrt-pau-acf-200.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ottenimento sequenziale record [mgr]    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "GN"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/cge/fls/ioc/obj/iofmgr"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-mgr                 .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test se 'at end'                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to wrt-pau-acf-300.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test sul massimo                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        rf-mgr-tip-arc       not  = w-lpa-tip-arc      or
                     rf-mgr-cod-arc       not  = w-lpa-cod-arc      or
                     rf-mgr-dat-rif       not  = w-lpa-dat-rif
                                                (w-wrt-pau-acf-ctr) or
                     rf-mgr-num-rif       not  = w-lpa-num-rif
                                                (w-wrt-pau-acf-ctr)
                     go to wrt-pau-acf-300.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Aggiornamento record [mgr]              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-lpa-dri-doc        to   rf-mgr-dat-rif         .
           move      w-lpa-nri-doc        to   rf-mgr-num-rif         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Update record [mgr]                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "UP"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/cge/fls/ioc/obj/iofmgr"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-mgr                 .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Unlock record [mgr]                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "RL"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/cge/fls/ioc/obj/iofmgr"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-mgr                 .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Riciclo su prossimo record [mgr]        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     wrt-pau-acf-200.
       wrt-pau-acf-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Unlock ultimo record [mgr]                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RL"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/cge/fls/ioc/obj/iofmgr"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-mgr                 .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo su scansione tabella partite            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     wrt-pau-acf-100.
       wrt-pau-acf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Aggiornamenti su scadenze fornitori generati dalla ge-    *
      *    * stione scadenze fornitori a fronte del movimento di re-   *
      *    * gistrazione fattura fornitore                             *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       wrt-mov-rsf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Set del flag di registrazione contabile presen- *
      *              * te o assente                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-wrt-mov-rsf-cge      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se si e' in modifica di una registrazione   *
      *                  * che non aveva generato nessun movimento     *
      *                  * contabile, non e' stato generato il movi-   *
      *                  * mento contabile e quindi non lo si deve ge- *
      *                  * nerare nemmeno per le relative scadenze     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if       (w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    =    "M"   ) and
                    (w-tes-drg-cge (1)    =    zero or
                     w-tes-npr-cge (1)    =    zero  )
                     move  "#"            to   w-wrt-mov-rsf-cge      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se registrazione contabile da eseguire *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   cge-scf-ftf-snx-000  thru cge-scf-ftf-snx-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se registrazione contabile da non eseguire, *
      *                  * set del flag                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cge-scf-ftf-snx    =    "N"
                     move  "#"            to   w-wrt-mov-rsf-cge      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione numero scadenza iniziale           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-npr-scf (1)    to   w-wrt-mov-rsf-wns      .
           subtract  1                    from w-wrt-mov-rsf-wns      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione numero protocollo iniziale di CGE  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-wrt-mov-rsf-cge    =    spaces
                     move  w-tes-npr-cge (1)
                                          to   w-wrt-mov-rsf-wnp      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ciclo di scansione su catena righe corpo 2      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Start su righe corpo 2 in catena movimenti  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ST"                 to   w-cat-rg2-ope          .
           move      1                    to   w-cat-rg2-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct2-000      thru cll-sub-ct2-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se start non valida : a fine ciclo          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg2-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to wrt-mov-rsf-999.
       wrt-mov-rsf-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Next su righe corpo in catena movimenti     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   w-cat-rg2-ope          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct2-000      thru cll-sub-ct2-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se at end : a fine ciclo                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg2-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to wrt-mov-rsf-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Movimento da buffer catena movimenti a work *
      *                  * per riga w-rg2                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rg2-buf        to   w-rg2                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se esiste il tipo operazione di regi-  *
      *                  * strazione per la scadenza fornitore         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg2-top-rsf (1)    =    zero
                     go to wrt-mov-rsf-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Incremento numero scadenza fornitore        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-wrt-mov-rsf-wns      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Incremento numero protocollo di contabili-  *
      *                  * ta'                                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-wrt-mov-rsf-cge    =    spaces and
                     w-rg2-cau-rsf (1)    not  = zero and
                     w-rg2-stc-rsf (1)    not  = zero
                     add   1              to   w-wrt-mov-rsf-wnp      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione record [sfs]                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "NO"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/scf/fls/ioc/obj/iofsfs"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-sfs                 .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Composizione record [sfs]                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Dati identificativi                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "IG"                 to   s-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
           move      s-dat                to   rf-sfs-ide-dat         .
           move      s-ute                to   rf-sfs-ide-ute         .
           move      s-fas                to   rf-sfs-ide-fas         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data registrazione movimento            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-dat-reg        to   rf-sfs-dtr-rgs         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data registrazione movimento di conta-  *
      *                      * bilita'                                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-wrt-mov-rsf-cge    =    spaces and
                     w-rg2-cau-rsf (1)    not  = zero and
                     w-rg2-stc-rsf (1)    not  = zero
                     move  w-tes-drg-cge (1)
                                          to   rf-sfs-drc-rgs         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero protocollo movimento di contabi- *
      *                      * lita'                                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-wrt-mov-rsf-cge    =    spaces and
                     w-rg2-cau-rsf (1)    not  = zero and
                     w-rg2-stc-rsf (1)    not  = zero
                     move  w-wrt-mov-rsf-wnp
                                          to   rf-sfs-npc-rgs         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero scadenza                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-wrt-mov-rsf-wns    to   rf-sfs-num-scf         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo scadenza                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg2-tip-scf (1)    to   rf-sfs-tip-scf         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo registrazione scadenza             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      01                   to   rf-sfs-trs-scf         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo valuta per la scadenza             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg2-tvl-scf (1)    to   rf-sfs-tvl-scf         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data di scadenza                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg2-dts-scf (1)    to   rf-sfs-dts-scf         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice fornitore                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-cod-fnt (1)    to   rf-sfs-cod-fnt         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice dipendenza del fornitore         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-dpz-fnt (1)    to   rf-sfs-dpz-fnt         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Inoltro pagamento al fornitore          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-inl-pgf (1)    to   rf-sfs-inl-scf         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sigla valuta per la scadenza            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-sgl-vlt (1)    to   rf-sfs-sgl-vlt         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero decimali per la valuta           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-dec-vlt (1)    to   rf-sfs-dec-vlt         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo di cambio                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-tdc-vlt (1)    to   rf-sfs-tdc-vlt         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Coefficiente di cambio                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-cdc-ftf (1)    to   rf-sfs-cdc-scf         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Importo scadenza in valuta              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg2-iiv-scf (1)    to   rf-sfs-iiv-scf         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Importo scadenza                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg2-imp-scf (1)    to   rf-sfs-imp-scf         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data documento di riferimento           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-ddo-ftf (1)    to   rf-sfs-dat-ddr         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero documento di riferimento         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-ndo-ftf (1)    to   rf-sfs-num-ddr         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo documento di riferimento           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-ope        =    0001 or
                     w-tes-tip-ope        =    0007 or
                     w-tes-tip-ope        =    0011 or
                     w-tes-tip-ope        =    0012 or
                     w-tes-tip-ope        =    0111 or
                     w-tes-tip-ope        =    0112
                     move  01             to   rf-sfs-tip-ddr
           else if   w-tes-tip-ope        =    0002 or
                     w-tes-tip-ope        =    0008 or
                     w-tes-tip-ope        =    0022 or
                     w-tes-tip-ope        =    0222
                     move  02             to   rf-sfs-tip-ddr
           else if   w-tes-tip-ope        =    0003 or
                     w-tes-tip-ope        =    0009 or
                     w-tes-tip-ope        =    0033 or
                     w-tes-tip-ope        =    0333
                     move  11             to   rf-sfs-tip-ddr
           else if   w-tes-tip-ope        =    0444
                     move  99             to   rf-sfs-tip-ddr         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Importo documento di riferimento        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-sgl-vlt (1)    =    c-sgl
                     move  w-tes-imp-ftf (1)
                                          to   rf-sfs-imp-ddr
           else      move  w-tes-iiv-ftf (1)
                                          to   rf-sfs-imp-ddr         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero rata documento di riferimento    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rg2-cur        to   rf-sfs-nra-ddr         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice ABI banca fornitore              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg2-abi-scf (1)    to   rf-sfs-abi-fnt         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice CAB banca fornitore              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg2-cab-scf (1)    to   rf-sfs-cab-fnt         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice banca estera del fornitore       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg2-bef-scf (1)    to   rf-sfs-cod-bef         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice conto corrente bancario o posta- *
      *                      * le                                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg2-tip-scf (1)    =    08
                     move  w-rg2-ccp-scf (1)
                                          to   rf-sfs-ccc-fnt
           else      move  w-rg2-ccc-scf (1)
                                          to   rf-sfs-ccc-fnt         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice nostra banca di appoggio         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg2-cbp-scf (1)    to   rf-sfs-cbp-nsb         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Si/No pagamento bloccato per la scaden- *
      *                      * za                                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg2-snx-pbl (1)    to   rf-sfs-snx-pbl         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tutti gli altri campi rimangono norma-  *
      *                      * lizzati                                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Scrittura record [sfs]                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "PT"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/scf/fls/ioc/obj/iofsfs"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-sfs                 .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riciclo su prossima scadenza                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     wrt-mov-rsf-100.
       wrt-mov-rsf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Annullamento dei movimenti di scadenze fornitori che era  *
      *    * stato a suo tempo generato a fronte del movimento di sca- *
      *    * denze fornitori di registrazione fattura fornitore        *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       del-mov-rsf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se numero prima scadenza a zero : uscita        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-npr-scf (2)    =    zero
                     go to del-mov-rsf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ciclo per tutti i movimenti registrati a parti- *
      *              * re dal numero scadenza iniziale                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione numero scadenza iniziale     *
      *                  * meno 1                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-npr-scf (2)    to   w-del-mov-rsf-nsi      .
           subtract  1                    from w-del-mov-rsf-nsi      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione numero scadenza finale       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-del-mov-rsf-nsi    to   w-del-mov-rsf-nsf      .
           add       w-tes-nrg-scf (2)    to   w-del-mov-rsf-nsf      .
       del-mov-rsf-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Incremento numero scadenza                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-del-mov-rsf-nsi      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se oltrepassato il massimo             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-del-mov-rsf-nsi    >    w-del-mov-rsf-nsf
                     go to del-mov-rsf-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Composizione chiave primaria                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-del-mov-rsf-nsi    to   rf-sfs-num-scf         .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Delete record [sfs]                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DE"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/scf/fls/ioc/obj/iofsfs"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-sfs                 .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riciclo per prossima cancellazione          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     del-mov-rsf-100.
       del-mov-rsf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Test Si/No aggiornamenti contabili da gestione scadenze   *
      *    * fornitori per i movimenti di registrazione scadenze for-  *
      *    * nitori                                                    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       cge-scf-ftf-snx-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se le personalizzazioni indicano che in ogni    *
      *              * caso gli aggiornamenti contabili non devono     *
      *              * essere eseguiti : uscita con 'N'                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-scf-snx-cge    =    "N"
                     move  "N"            to   w-cge-scf-ftf-snx
                     go to cge-scf-ftf-snx-999.
       cge-scf-ftf-snx-025.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se il codice causale contabile per il tipo ope- *
      *              * razione di registrazione fattura fornitore e' a *
      *              * zero : uscita con 'N'                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-top-cau-cge
                    (w-top-ele-inx)       =    zero
                     move  "N"            to   w-cge-scf-ftf-snx
                     go to cge-scf-ftf-snx-999.
       cge-scf-ftf-snx-050.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Altrimenti si esce con 'S'                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-cge-scf-ftf-snx      .
       cge-scf-ftf-snx-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Find su archivio [sfs]                                    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       fnd-arc-sff-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione flag di selezione               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   w-fnd-arc-sff-sel      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se programma di interrogazione gia' attivo :    *
      *              * uscita senza alcuna azione                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "P?"                 to   s-ope                  .
           move      "pscf3010"           to   s-pro                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
           if        s-liv                not  = zero
                     go to fnd-arc-sff-999.
       fnd-arc-sff-025.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Scrittura variabile di i.p.c. 'tip-int' per il  *
      *              * livello successivo per il tipo di interrogazio- *
      *              * ne                                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "PV"                 to   s-ope                  .
           move      "tip-int"            to   s-var                  .
           move      "+"                  to   s-dop                  .
           move      "A"                  to   s-tip                  .
           move      10                   to   s-car                  .
           move      "INTFTF    "         to   s-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
       fnd-arc-sff-050.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Scrittura variabile di i.p.c. 'cod-fnt' per il  *
      *              * livello successivo per il codice fornitore      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se valore a zero : no scrittura             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-fnd-arc-sff-fnt    =    zero
                     go to fnd-arc-sff-075.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Scrittura effettiva                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "PV"                 to   s-ope                  .
           move      "cod-fnt"            to   s-var                  .
           move      "+"                  to   s-dop                  .
           move      "N"                  to   s-tip                  .
           move      07                   to   s-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   s-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   s-sgn                  .
           move      w-fnd-arc-sff-fnt    to   s-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
       fnd-arc-sff-075.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Scrittura variabile di i.p.c. 'dpz-fnt' per il  *
      *              * livello successivo per la dipendenza fornitore  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se valore a spaces : no scrittura           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-fnd-arc-sff-dpf    =    spaces
                     go to fnd-arc-sff-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se codice fornitore a zero : no scrittura   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-fnd-arc-sff-fnt    =    zero
                     go to fnd-arc-sff-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Scrittura effettiva                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "PV"                 to   s-ope                  .
           move      "dpz-fnt"            to   s-var                  .
           move      "+"                  to   s-dop                  .
           move      "A"                  to   s-tip                  .
           move      04                   to   s-car                  .
           move      w-fnd-arc-sff-dpf    to   s-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
       fnd-arc-sff-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Scrittura variabile di i.p.c. 'tip-ftf' per il  *
      *              * livello successivo per il tipo fattura fornito- *
      *              * re                                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se valore non ammesso : no scritture suc-   *
      *                  * cessive                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-fnd-arc-sff-tip    <    01 or
                     w-fnd-arc-sff-tip    >    03
                     go to fnd-arc-sff-150.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Scrittura effettiva                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "PV"                 to   s-ope                  .
           move      "tip-ftf"            to   s-var                  .
           move      "+"                  to   s-dop                  .
           move      "N"                  to   s-tip                  .
           move      02                   to   s-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   s-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   s-sgn                  .
           move      w-fnd-arc-sff-tip    to   s-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
       fnd-arc-sff-125.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Scrittura variabile di i.p.c. 'tpv-ftf' per il  *
      *              * livello successivo per il tipo provenienza fat- *
      *              * tura fornitore                                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
